l of happiness&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The first step to increasing your level of happiness is realizing you can. This is where a lot of people get tripped up. For the vast majority of people, some of their happiness—probably a lot more than they think—is in their control.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
